341
00:20:42,880 --> 00:20:43,480
But she isn't

342
00:20:43,510 --> 00:20:44,750
the Dark Clan member we're after.

343
00:20:45,440 --> 00:20:46,310
I see.

344
00:20:47,550 --> 00:20:49,750
