399
00:23:58,440 --> 00:24:00,200
For someone unafraid of death,

400
00:24:00,880 --> 00:24:02,160
keeping him locked up is pointless.

401
00:24:03,070 --> 00:24:03,750
Master,

402
00:24:05,200 --> 00:24:06,550
