503
00:28:37,920 --> 00:28:39,270
Then I'll devote myself to it fully.

504
00:28:40,920 --> 00:28:42,030
Here's the Half-Day Glory.

505
00:28:42,550 --> 00:28:43,030
Take it.

506
00:28:44,440 --> 00:28:45,880
My act is flawless,

507
00:28:46,200 --> 00:28:47,720
