523
00:29:32,000 --> 00:29:33,030
Too bad we got off

524
00:29:33,790 --> 00:29:35,350
on the wrong foot again.

525
00:29:36,970 --> 00:29:37,760
But that's fine.

526
00:29:38,350 --> 00:29:39,110
This time,

527
00:29:39,750 --> 00:29:40,750
