00:31:36,030 --> 00:31:37,160
She'd probably beat me up for that.

554
00:31:41,750 --> 00:31:42,680
Xuanling,

555
00:31:43,310 --> 00:31:45,400
about what happened today, I misunderstood you,

556
00:31:45,640 --> 00:31:46,550
