774
00:41:32,360 --> 00:41:33,000
I believe

775
00:41:35,630 --> 00:41:37,150
Saint Fajian, with his virtue and standing,

776
00:41:38,070 --> 00:41:39,070
is the best candidate.

777
00:41:48,880 --> 00:41:50,000
Thank you, Mr. Xie,

778
00:41:51,000 --> 00:41:52,800
